description:
The mission continues. Sending in a second wave, this time 99 Elite Lunar Buddies equipped with unique set of rank, badges, helmet logos and backgrounds. Mission parameter seek and destroy possible alien FEES base on the darkside of the MOON.
Who will mint the super rare Buddy with Shimmer background or 3d color logo.

Elite Lunar Buddy specs
5 different badges with the 2 head eagle at only 10 % rarity
6 different backgrounds, with shimmer background at only 5% rarity
5 different ranks on arm, with stars on top at only 10% rarity
5 different IOTA logo on helmet, with 3D color at only 5% rarity
name: IOTA Lunar Buddies - Elite Second Wave
